  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: October 13, 2025</p>

  <p>Smart Reel Poster (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our app or related services.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We may collect your TikTok account information (such as user ID and access token) only after you explicitly authorize our app via TikTok’s official OAuth process. We do not collect or store your personal data beyond what is required to upload videos on your behalf.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>Your TikTok access token is used solely to upload videos and manage captions based on your authorization. We do not share or sell this information to any third party.</p>

  <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
  <p>We do not permanently store any user-generated content or access tokens. Tokens are kept securely in temporary server memory only for the duration of your active session.</p>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>Our app integrates with TikTok APIs to publish videos on your behalf. All API interactions comply with TikTok Developer Terms of Service.</p>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You can revoke app access at any time through your TikTok account settings. Once revoked, we no longer have permission to access or post to your account.</p>

  <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <strong>support@smartreelposter.app</strong>.</p>
